  "title": "Technical Operator",
  "description": "<p>🌟🔧Join our team in providing the full support in the production of the sub assembly, main assembly, testing and packing of the products being assigned!</p><p><strong>Job responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>Assemble, test and pack the product according to the approved processes and procedures.</li><li>Support the technicians, operators, engineers for the trouble shooting.</li><li>Ensure that the working area is maintaining a good 5S and always considering and practicing safety procedures on the line.</li><li>Provide Support to the Engineer for the analysis, ECO and process improvement.</li><li>Provide support to other production when the situation calls for, support in the packing in the case of urgent requirement for the shipment or in the absence of packers.</li><li>Ensure that the production schedule is meet accordingly.</li><li>Assist to ensure the production inventory is accurate and aging inventory is disposed timely.</li><li>Other responsibilities that may be assigned from time to time.</li></ul><p><strong>Job requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>NTC2 Electronics Servicing</li><li>Experience in Manufacturing of Life Science Devices or Electronics/Electrical Products</li><li>Meticulous; pay attention to details</li><li>Team Player with positive attitude</li></ul>",
